PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?country WHERE {
  wd:Q3542 wdt:P403 * ?bodyOfWater .
  ?bodyOfWater wdt:P17 ?country .
  FILTER ( ?country IN ( wd:Q79 , wd:Q262 , wd:Q1033 , wd:Q1049 , wd:Q1009 , wd:Q657 , wd:Q912 , wd:Q965 , wd:Q1025 , wd:Q1041 ) )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?coordinateLocation ?continent WHERE {
  wd:Q783 wdt:P625 ?coordinateLocation .
  wd:Q783 wdt:P361 ?continent .
  FILTER ( ?continent = wd:Q27611 )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?actor WHERE {
  ?actor wdt:P181 wd:Q3036775 .
  ?actor rdfs:label 'Janel Moloney' @en
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?actor WHERE {
  wd:Q23831 wdt:P161 ?actor .
  ?actor wdt:P181 ?character .
  ?character rdfs:label 'Dwight Schrute' @en
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?book ?date WHERE {
  ?book wdt:P50 wd:Q207 ; wdt:P577 ?date .
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?date )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?city ?population WHERE {
  ?city wdt:P31 wd:Q515 ; wdt:P17 wd:Q29 ; wdt:P1082 ?population .
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?population )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?cupWin ?year WHERE {
  wd:Q203008 wdt:P166 wd:Q1139735 .
  wd:Q203008 wdt:P585 ?year
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?year )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?adminEntity ?coordinates ?specificLocation WHERE {
  wd:Q1319988 wdt:P131 ?adminEntity .
  wd:Q1319988 wdt:P625 ?coordinates .
  wd:Q1319988 wdt:P276 ?specificLocation .
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
SELECT ?startDate WHERE {
  wd:Q33866 p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q11696 ; pq:P580 ?startDate .
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?character WHERE {
  wd:Q358345 wdt:P161 ?film .
  ?film wdt:P179 wd:Q462 .
  ?character wdt:P161 wd:Q358345 .
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?airport ?airportLabel WHERE {
  ?airport wdt:P31 wd:Q1248784 ; wdt:P17 wd:Q30 .
  ?airport wdt:P131 ?city .
  ?city rdfs:label ?cityLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?cityLabel ) = 'en' ) .
  FILTER ( ?cityLabel = 'New York City' ) .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?airport rdfs:label ?airportLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?airportLabel ) = 'en' )
  }
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?start ?end WHERE {
  wd:Q9640 wdt:P39 ?position .
  ?position wdt:P31 wd:Q11699 .
  ?position pq:P580 ?start .
  ?position pq:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= '1961-01-20T00:00:00Z' ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?end >= '1963-11-22T00:00:00Z' ^^ xsd:dateTime )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?voiceActor WHERE {
  wd:Q2265493 wdt:P161 ?voiceActor .
  ?voiceActor rdfs:label ?label
  FILTER ( LANG( ?label ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT ?pm ?pmLabel ?start ?end WHERE {
  wd:Q29 p:P6 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P6 ?pm .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?start .
  ?statement pq:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= '2011-12-31' ^^ xsd:date && ?end >= '2011-01-01' ^^ xsd:date ) OPTIONAL {
    ?pm rdfs:label ?pmLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?pmLabel ) = 'en' )
  }
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?team ?award ?position ?event ?occupation ?sport WHERE {
  wd:Q193637 wdt:P54 ?team .
  wd:Q193637 wdt:P166 ?award .
  wd:Q193637 wdt:P413 ?position .
  wd:Q193637 wdt:P1344 ?event .
  wd:Q193637 wdt:P106 ?occupation .
  wd:Q193637 wdt:P641 ?sport .
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT ?media ?character WHERE {
  ?media p:P161 [ ps:P161 wd:Q16297 ; pq:P410 ?character ] .
  ?character rdfs:label 'James T. Kirk' @en
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?country WHERE {
  wd:Q855 wdt:P39 ?position .
  ?position wdt:P17 ?country
}
LIMIT 1
